    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃、結成した時の葵は今よりも自由気ままで\nよく私と衝突していたわ",
      "startTime": 6.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "打ち合わせをすっぽかして勝手に練習していたり、好み\nじゃない振り付けや衣装に、いろいろと文句を言ったり",
      "startTime": 13.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、パフォーマンスは完璧だったけれど\n私もその時は今よりその……尖っていたから",
      "startTime": 21.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "つい葵を厳しく指導し過ぎてしまって……\n私達の関係は、デビュー早々ぎくしゃくしていたわ",
      "startTime": 31.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですか？　リズノワのステージは\nデビュー当時からずっと息がピッタリじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 39.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ダンスに関してはね\nでも、ステージを降りた途端、またすぐに喧嘩よ",
      "startTime": 46.4360996247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "見えないところで、そんなことになっていたとは\n……全然気付きませんでしたよ",
      "startTime": 55.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "葵も私も、まだ互いを理解出来ていなかったのかもね\nそんな中私達の初のワンマンライブが決まったんだけど",
      "startTime": 63.2521086057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "お願いよ、葵。我がままばかり言わないでちょうだい\n「こんなひらひらした衣装、着たくない」なんて……",
      "startTime": 74.7521086057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "貴方の言う通り、少し踊りにくいかもしれないけど\n今から衣装を作り直すなんて出来ないわよ",
      "startTime": 82.0854419391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、怒らなかったんですね。俺の名刺を捨てた\n莉央さんならもっとキツいことを言いそうですけど……",
      "startTime": 92.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "し、失礼ね！\n私の方が葵よりずっと大人なのよ？",
      "startTime": 97.9365303357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "葵の気持ちを分かってあげなきゃいけない、と思って\nちゃんと優しくさとしたに決まってるじゃない！",
      "startTime": 104.8031970024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、葵は納得出来なかったみたいで……\n何も言わずに、その場を飛び出してしまって",
      "startTime": 112.5031970024,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5696.8029976000025,
          "startTime": 118.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "それから、当時まだバンプロに在籍していた三枝さんと\n私とで、慌てて葵を探し回ったわ",
      "startTime": 122.3031970024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "葵、どこにいるのー！？　葵ー！\nどうしよう、私がムキになり過ぎたせいだわ……",
      "startTime": 130.3031970024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "当時、葵はまだ小学生ですから、心配だったでしょう\nそれで……葵は見つかったんですか？",
      "startTime": 140.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ……葵の行きそうな場所は全部探したんだけど\n見つけられなかったわ",
      "startTime": 148.3632195155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "今考えたら、公園で踊ってるって\n分かるけれど、当時はまだ知らなかったから",
      "startTime": 153.0632103602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-shj001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央。後は俺が探しておくから今日はもう家に帰って\n休んだ方がいい。そんなに深刻に考えるな",
      "startTime": 164.7965436935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さん……でも……！\n……分かりました。ご迷惑掛けて、すみません",
      "startTime": 174.1965436935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "私も大人だし、葵にばかり構っていられないから\n一人で家に帰ったのよ",
      "startTime": 184.6298770268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "そんな時よ。私の部屋のインターホンが鳴ったのは\n部屋の前に立っていたのは……葵だった",
      "startTime": 192.1298770268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "葵がドアを開けた瞬間のことは、今でも覚えてるわ\nその時の葵ったら、どんな表情してたと思う？",
      "startTime": 201.6965345382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "息を切らせて、泣きそうな顔をしてて……\nあんなに必死な葵、今になるまで見たことがないわ",
      "startTime": 210.2298729578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "葵ったら、私に直接謝るために\n三枝さんから私の住所まで聞いたらしくて",
      "startTime": 218.8632062911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_02-rio022.m4a",
